We Only Handle Mesothelioma & Asbestos Lung Cancer Cases





Unlike large firms that handle asbestos cases as part of a much broader
	 practice, since 1990 our practice has been dedicated solely to mesothelioma
	 and asbestos lung cancer cases.


We Never...

Bundle our clients' claims with non-malignant disease claims
Use a mass-produced,  generic strategy.



We Always...

Return phone calls and emails promptly and professionally
Tailor your representation to meet your unique needs and priorities













	Our responsive, individualized attention to our client’s medical
	 and legal needs together
	 with customized representation is what sets us apart.



