Our Team













Our Team





Worthington & Caron, PC: Asbestos Lawyers for Life

Worthington & Caron, PC has been committed to
	empowering mesothelioma patients and their families since 1990. The firm, comprised
	 of Attorney
	Roger G. Worthington and
	John M. Caron, is based in California and handles asbestos-related mesothelioma cases
	 throughout the United States.

Medical Empowerment

	People who choose Worthington & Caron after receiving a mesothelioma cancer
	diagnosis become more than just our clients. Our attorneys are not just your legal
	 advocates. We are here to advocate for the best possible
	treatment options. By connecting you to leading mesothelioma physicians and emerging
	clinical trials, we give you the medical empowerment you deserve after a diagnosis.

Legal Empowerment
Worthington & Caron, PC has practiced nothing but asbestos-related
	 litigation since 1990. Our team is completely dedicated to these cases
	 for life – hence our motto “Asbestos Lawyers for Life.”
	 We tailor our representation to each individual client and his or her
	 unique needs. Our clients are never ignored, never marginalized, and never
	 left on their own.
Commitment to Research
The team at Worthington & Caron, PC has personally donated thousands
	 of dollars to mesothelioma research. Attorney Roger Worthington even helped
	 found the Mesothelioma Applied Research Foundation, a non-profit organization
	 committed to advancing mesothelioma research for early detection and improved
	 patient prognosis.
For Us, It’s Personal

	Worthington & Caron’s team of attorneys have personally experienced
	 the effects of
	asbestos cancer. Roger Worthington’s father, Punch, battled asbestos cancer. We
	 want what every other mesothelioma patient and their family wants –
	 a cure. We fight for mesothelioma patients for hope – for life.

More Than $2.5 Billion Recovered

	When looking for a mesothelioma advocate to have in your corner, results
	 matter. Not only do we passionately care about advancing mesothelioma
	 research and empowering patients, but that passion also translates into
	 results. Worthington & Caron’s attorneys have
	recovered more than $2.5 billion in verdicts and settlements for mesothelioma
		 cancer patients.


To learn more about Attorney Roger Worthington or Attorney John Caron,
				 read their complete biographies.  


John M. Caron 
